snippet.title: Judge Orders Depp to Stay Away From Amber Heard
snippet.description:
A judge has ordered Johnny Depp to stay 100 yards away from his estranged wife, actress Amber Heard. Heard said in a sworn declaration that Depp threw her cellphone at her during a fight Saturday, striking her cheek and eye. (May 27)
